high_descs: Head to ward the countertop then turn right side.
Pick the bread from the right side.
Turn around and take right to reach the microwave.
Put the bread on the Microwave oven
Take the bread and turn around the right side of the diningtable.
Then put the bread on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the Bread cooked in put it on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn your right side and take a walk and enter into the kitchen which is in the right side and walk towards the end of the room after passing the countertop.
Take a bread loaf from the top of the counter which is next to the oven
Turn towards your left and stand in front of the microwave
Open the oven door and put the bread inside the oven and close the door. After some minutes take out the bread and close the door.
Turn left and walk few steps and again turn towards your left side and head towards the diningtable
Place the bread loaf on the diningtable next to spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place the bread on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn right and then proceed to turn left towards the counter top
Pick up bread from the counter top
Turn left and go straight, turn right towards the microwave
Place bread inside microwave and then take it out
Turn left and head straight, turn left and make a turn left and then proceed to turn left towards the dining table
Place bread on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Heating bread on microwave and placing it in dining table
